                  </hi>. I am a carpenter, of Wick, Sussex—I employed the bankrupt last year to do work for me; this account, beginning in March, 1869, correctly describes it—it was done at those dates, as far as I know—on 10th July, 1849, I paid him 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., and have the receipt (<hi rend="italic">produced</hi>)—I am still indebted to him for the balance, 19<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. 10 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—I have never had the bill.</p>
