                  </hi>. I live at Littlehampton—I employed the bankrupt to do some work, and owed him 2<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>. at the time of his bankruptcy.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18700502-name-120" type="witnessName">
